channel.description:
Hey everybody,
This is Amazing Magda and I'm presenting you "Magda Conquers Black Mesa" show. A very feminine and quite weird and sometimes crazy *conquest* of the game! Plus a foreign accent.
Episode 1: [url='https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=S5xm2suH4-A']https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=S5xm2suH4-A[/url]
Epsiode 2: [url='https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zxkeq86I05w']https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zxkeq86I05w[/url]
I got inspired with "mind" series on YouTube. There is definietley too little grils doing this. Hope you enjoy it!
Gimmie thumbs up and subscribe! :wink:
I'm currently working on the third episode. I appreciate your support and feedback. Thank you!
